manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: TOTE IT ON A GETAWAY Long weekend to a sunny destination coming up? Quick weekend trip to visit some friends? We got you covered! The Oversized Tote has room for all the things: your makeup bag, change of clothes, toiletries, and more! There’s plenty of room for it all. TOTE IT TO THE BEACH It’s got room aplenty for a few beach towels, sunscreen, flipflop, snacks and more! Use the long straps and throw it over your shoulder while you look for the perfect spot to lay in the sun! TOTE IT AROUND TOWN Doing some heavy shopping? No one likes multiple trips packing the car. The XXL Tote has the room to sufficiently fit everything you’ve got! Overload it with all the essentials so your day running errands is effortless. TOTE IT TO SPORTING EVENTS Go ahead! Throw the kiddo’s soccer ball, cleats, shin guards, change of clothes, and some water bottles in there. The XXL Tote can handle it all to prepare you for a whole day at the field.

THE ONLY JUMBO TOTE THAT CAN CARRY ANYTHING AND EVERYTHING! OVERSIZED GROCERIES Ready to do some serious grocery shopping? Made with durable water-resistant cotton canvas for your heaviest loads, this XXL tote holds up to 50 lbs.! Ditch the paper or plastic for the reusable All The Things bag. LAUNDRY/SEASONAL CLOTHES Perfect for toting clothes to and from the laundry mat - avoid large plastic laundry bins! Free your hands and sling this over your shoulder! HOLIDAY GIFT BAG Use this stylish oversized tote bag to easily deliver all your holiday gifts in one trip! You’ll be more popular than St. Nick. TOYS AND CRAFTS Keep your home spaces neat and organized. Store your kiddo’s toys and crafts in All The Things!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Spacious and Sturdy
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. A great bag for the poolside, beach visits, overnights, whatever you need a huge bag for. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality and size!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this bag to carry my massage therapy supplies. I have gone through 3 other bags before this one in the past decade, so Im pretty rough on them. I hope this one lasts longer. It's quite durable and seems to be made well. Im happy with how much it can hold. It's quite sizable. There are plenty of smaller travel bags out there. For this size, this bag was the best option I found. I recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I LOVE THIS BAG
reviews.reviewText: I LOVE this bag!First, I have to give a disclaimer... I have a weird obsession with bags. But, that should also let you know how great this bag is because I go through a lot of bags and there are few that I feel the need to rave about.I use Ikea bags regularly because I love how big and sturdy they are. I use them for everything and bring them everywhere. But... they're bright blue, plastic-ish bags. So I was looking for an alternative that would hold a lot of stuff that I could carry here and there. I read the reviews and thought I would check this one out. And, the photos were quite impressive of someone carrying this monstrous thing.When I opened the package I felt this wave of disappointment thinking, "This isn't nearly as big as it looked." But when I took it out, opened it up, and put some stuff in it... wow! It's huge! Then I realized that not only was it huge, but it's really well made. It seems really sturdy, it's canvas, which I really like, and I'm already absolutely loving it and planning on how I'm going to start parting with my 30+ Ikea bags that are all over my house. I plan to buy a couple more of these, so I can keep one in the car and one at my office for comfort reasons and that will let me finally let go of most of these ugly Ikea bags. I can also totally see giving these as gifts because who doesn't love a huge tote bag? I mean this thing would come in handy for just about anyone.If I had 2 (tiny) complaints, I would love to see more patterns (I like subdued patterns, like tone on tone paisleys, etc vs. bright patterns) and I would love an outside pocket or 2. But other than that, this thing is amazing and I'm so glad I bought it! Well worth the money!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I like this bag so much!
reviews.reviewText: This bag is great! I carry a lot of things to and from work and it is extremely durable. The size is as shown and there are pockets inside that help with organization. The quality is good and the zippers work well and seem to be sturdy. The material also seems to be durable carrying a bunch of stuff that are all different shapes and sizes. Could probably work well for traveling also but it would be too big to fit under an airplane seat.
Weekend/beach/shopping - this bag works for everything. Seems like good quality and has LOTS of space. Highly recommend.
